short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Synchronize browser bookmarks from a GitHub repository

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Share a common set of bookmarks across a team or organization by storing them in a simple JSON structure in a GitHub repository, and have them then automatically synchronized to your bookmarks toolbar.

Supports both repositories hosted on GitHub.com, as well as GitHub Enterprise Server instances.
